articles.title: Mark Zuckerberg's wife Priscilla Chan welcomes their third child, a daughter named Aurelia - Daily Mail
articles.description: Mark Zuckerberg and his 38-year-old wife Priscilla have welcomed their third child. The power couple made their announcement on Instagram on Friday morning. The child is a daughter named Aurelia.
articles.content:
Mark Zuckerberg and his 38-year-old wife Priscilla have welcomed their third child together.
